General.Name: IT Competence Group SE
General.Description: audius SE, through its subsidiaries, provides information technology (IT) consulting and software solutions in Germany. It offers IT consulting services, including IT infrastructure, operational planning, data management and IT network planning. The company also provides security and audit services, data protection, software consulting, consulting, and Microsoft SharePoint; and managed services, audius service desk, audius.cloud, onsite, professional, and software support services and software, such as Microsoft dynamics 365, industry solutions, customized software, mobility platform dashface, interface adis, and Microsoft 365. The company was formerly known as IT Competence Group SE and changed its name to audius SE in October 2020. audius SE was founded in 1991 and is headquartered in Weinstadt, Germany. audius SE is a subsidiary of audius AG.
